=Introduction=
The '''Item Shop (アイテム屋)''' is a main menu function where you can purchase resources, unlocks or useful items. The two tabs on the left correspond to the [[Inventory]] (アイテム一覧) and [[Furniture|Furniture Store]] (家具屋さん).

<div style="margin:20px 10px 30px; padding:10px; font-size:16px; background:#cfc; text-align:center; border:1px solid #5c5; font-weight:bold;">If you're looking to buy yourself some in-game items<br />using real money, see the new [[Shop/Purchasing|Purchasing Guide]].</div>

=Shop Contents=
===Important Notes===
* '''Consumables''' such as {{IR}} Repair Buckets, {{IC}} Instant Construction, and {{DM}} Development Materials are capped at '''3,000'''.
** Attempting to purchase any more than this will result in the items being lost.
* Items from seasonal mini-events like [[Saury]] are capped at '''99'''.
* More items can be accessed by clicking the '''Specials Corner (特撰コーナー)''' arrow at the bottom right.
** Clicking on the '''Regular Corner (レギュラーコーナー)''' arrow will take you back to the normal shop selection.
* There will be '''no confirmation''' when using a Dock Key. Please be careful where you click after you have purchased one or you may waste it.
* It is '''very inadvisable''' to purchase resources from the [[#Regular Corner|Regular Corner]] because of the bad value. 

